<expan>ſelb<ex>er</ex></expan> wol waiſt / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_201_line_1576594428209_8420"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ṽ . <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Thome
